{"type":"message","id":"ac14370f","parentId":"d4a2a80d","timestamp":"2026-06-01T15:51:52.838Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"Good work on the task restore. A few follow-ups:\n\n1. Commit and push the task system fixes if you haven't already\n\n2. The progress bar overhaul — did that get completed? Real agent \n   activity instead of fake CSS animation?\n\n3. Once everything is committed, I have a new build from Replit \n   ready to integrate. It's on the WD MyCloud at:\n   /Volumes/Public/openclaw-agent-backup/crew-new/\n   \n   The build has:\n   - New canvas-based agent sprites (no PNG files) — all 4 agents \n     drawn live on <canvas> with idle/working/walking poses\n   - Crew visits — agents walking between rooms with EN ROUTE labels\n   - Station mood lighting — pulsing tint based on station state\n   - Celebration overlay — confetti on task completion\n   - Empty state cameos — themed holding states\n   - Bug fixes: OKLCH→HSL for canvas, duplicate sprite suppression, \n     hub orb color fix\n\n   I'll send the full integration prompt after you confirm current \n   work is committed.\n\nStatus check: all committed? Board clear? Ready for the next build?","timestamp":1780329112705,"idempotencyKey":"86058dfc-0ead-407e-9d66-c6382948e61b:user"}}
