{"type":"message","id":"af51f40f","parentId":"8b9a8c60","timestamp":"2026-06-01T15:54:25.952Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Wait — but looking more carefully, the `calculateProgress` function is still the old fake one (`elapsed / 60000 * 10`). The diff only adds stall detection and color changes on top. The comment says \"real progress (not fake animation)\" but the underlying function still simulates. Let me check if there's more to come or if this is intentional:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"eb5b22dc-fa29-499e-aa82-7cdb596e04d3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check the types.ts diff too\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git show HEAD -- src/lib/server-data/types.ts | head -40"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Check the types.ts diff too\\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard && git show HEAD -- src/lib/server-data/types.ts | head -40\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":213,"output":128,"cacheRead":66688,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":67029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780329246238,"responseId":"gen-1780329246-2Eqaf7hN0tfeQrp6rNko"}}
