{"type":"message","id":"98f53712","parentId":"386b4130","timestamp":"2026-06-01T15:55:11.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK — here's the full status:\n\n---\n\n**1. Commits ✅**\n- Workspace: committed task data restore + archive policy → `0550357`\n- MC Dashboard: committed progress bar overhaul → `234ae46`, **pushed to GitHub**\n\n**2. Progress Bar Overhaul — partially done ✅**\n- What's in: stall detection, progress bar color states (grey→green→amber), new type fields (`currentStep`, `lastActivity`, `stalledAt`, `stallNotified`)\n- What's **not** done yet: `calculateProgress()` still uses the old time-based estimation (`elapsed / 60000 * 10`). It's still a fake simulation, just with better display. The infrastructure is in place for agents to report real progress, but agents aren't actually calling `onUpdate` with `currentStep` / `lastActivity` yet.\n\n**3. Rebuild Build — not available yet ❌**\n- `/Volumes/Public/openclaw-agent-backup/crew-new/` doesn't exist\n- The WD MyCloud volume (`/Volumes/Public/`) isn't mounted\n\nOnce you've got the build uploaded to the MyCloud, drop it in and I'll handle the integration. Ready when you are."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":357,"output":276,"cacheRead":67200,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":67833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780329279583,"responseId":"gen-1780329279-d1n3fbsDJhTeDhtzWIhI"}}
