{"type":"message","id":"65531c85","parentId":"2fc3a5fd","timestamp":"2026-06-01T20:42:07.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What you're describing is **screen control** or **remote desktop control** — specifically, controlling your Mac's cursor and interacting with the UI programmatically.\n\nHere's what I can and can't do:\n\n**What I can do today:**\n- **Browser automation** — I have a `browser-automation` skill that can control web pages via the OpenClaw browser tool (click, type, navigate, screenshot)\n- **Shell commands** — I can run scripts, including AppleScript, which *can* control the mouse and keyboard on macOS\n\n**What I can't do (yet):**\n- Direct screen/mouse control of your Mac desktop — there's no built-in tool for me to move your cursor, click UI elements, or interact with native macOS apps\n\n**The closest option right now:** I can use **AppleScript** via `osascript` to do some cursor control and UI scripting. For example:\n\n```bash\n# Move mouse\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to set position of mouse pointer to {500, 300}'\n\n# Click\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to click at {500, 300}'\n\n# Type text\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to keystroke \"hello\"'\n```\n\nBut this is clunky, fragile, and requires Accessibility permissions. It's not a great experience for repeatable tasks.\n\n**Better options to explore:**\n1. **VNC/remote desktop integration** — if OpenClaw ever adds a screen control tool, this would be the proper way\n2. **Shortcuts app on iPhone** — you could create iOS Shortcuts that trigger Mac actions, and I could invoke them\n3. **Browser-based control** — if the thing you want to automate is a web app, I can control it directly via the browser tool\n\nWhat's the actual task you're trying to automate? There might be a better path than cursor control."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":85937,"output":420,"cacheRead":1024,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":87381,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780346503572,"responseId":"gen-1780346504-RwbafvHYsFrLnsBxHUf8"}}
