{"type":"message","id":"50c72ab3","parentId":"d61c2f9f","timestamp":"2026-06-01T21:34:17.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"bb5e20ca-7fd0-4676-89d0-95fd54fa3e97","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"eway may be in a crash loop.\",tags:$R[21]=[\"gateway\",\"crash-loop\",\"session-takeover\",\"gateway-monitor\"],timeline:$R[22]=[$R[23]={ts:\"2026-06-01T07:23:16.000Z\",message:\"Auto-detected by gateway-monitor\",actor:\"system\"}],actions:$R[24]=[]},$R[25]={id:\"INC-038\",title:\"Tasks stuck In Progress — 3 tasks with no recent activity\",severity:\"P3\",status:\"TRIAGE\",owner:\"monkey\",acknowledged:!1,escalated:!1,opened:\"2026-06-01T07:23:15.000Z\",lastActivity:\"2026-06-01T07:23:15.000Z\",summary:\"3 tasks are in In Progress state. Tasks without activity for extended periods should be reviewed.\",tags:$R[26]=[\"tasks\",\"stale\",\"in-progress\",\"task-monitor\"],timeline:$R[27]=[$R[28]={ts:\"2026-06-01T07:23:15.000Z\",message:\"Auto-detected by task-monitor\",actor:\"system\"}],actions:$R[29]=[]},$R[30]={id:\"INC-037\",title:\"Daily Station Check duplicate cron causing nightly token burn\",severity:\"P2\",status:\"RESOLVED\",owner:\"monkey\",acknowledged:!0,escalated:!1,opened:\"2026-05-21T23:00:00.000Z\",resolved:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",lastActivity:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",summary:\"Cron job dae7406b (Daily Station Check) was an agentTurn job that burned tokens every night at 23:00 BST from May 21–31. It was supposed to be disabled when the shell-only LaunchAgent replacement (com.openclaw.daily-station-check) was created, but it remained enabled. Each run spawned an isolated AI session that hit the 120s timeout in model-call-started phase, costing tokens with zero useful output. 4 consecutive errors recorded. Root cause: old cron was never deleted when LaunchAgent was deployed. Fixed by permanently deleting cron job dae7406b on 2026-06-01.\",tags:$R[31]=[\"cron\",\"token-burn\",\"duplicate\",\"agentTurn\",\"timeout\"],timeline:$R[32]=[$R[33]={ts:\"2026-05-21T23:00:00.000Z\",message:\"First recorded failure of dae7406b — agentTurn timeout in model-call-started. LaunchAgent replacement already existed but old cron was never deleted.\",actor:\"system\"},$R[34]={ts:\"2026-05-31T21:51:00.000Z\",message:\"Andre reports Daily Station Check has been 'fixed' three times and still burning tokens. Investigation launched.\",actor:\"Andre\"},$R[35]={ts:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",message:\"Root cause confirmed: dae7406b was enabled the entire time alongside the LaunchAgent. Cron job permanently deleted. Added FRAMEWORK.md gotcha: always DELETE old cron when replacing with LaunchAgent.\",actor:\"Space Monkey\"}],actions:$R[36]=[$R[37]={label:\"Delete old cron job dae7406b\",description:\"Permanently delete the agentTurn cron, not just disable it\",status:\"completed\",completedAt:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",completedBy:\"Space Monkey\"},$R[38]={label:\"Add FRAMEWORK.md gotcha\",description:\"Document the rule: DELETE old cron when replacing with LaunchAgent\",status:\"completed\",completedAt:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",completedBy:\"Space Monkey\"},$R[39]={label:\"Verify LaunchAgent is sole mechanism\",description:\"Confirm com.openclaw.daily-station-check is the only daily check mechanism and it's shell-only\",status:\"completed\",completedAt:\"2026-06-01T07:31:00.000Z\",completedBy:\"Space Monkey\"}]},$R[40]={id:\"INC-036\",title:\"Rate limit exhaustion — 11 429 errors in gateway log\",severity:\"P2\",status:\"TRIAGE\",owner:\"lifesupport\",acknowledged:!1,escalated:!1,opened:\"2026-05-31T21:51:22.000Z\",lastActivity:\"2026-05-31T21:51:22.000Z\",summary:\"Gateway log shows 11 rate limit (429) errors. Free model pool may be exhausted.\",tags:$R[41]=[\"rate-limit\",\"429\",\"models\",\"rate-monitor\"],timeline:$R[42]=[$R[43]={ts:\"2026-05-31T21:51:22.000Z\",message:\"Auto-detected by rate-monitor\",actor:\"system\"}],actions:$R[44]=[]},$R[45]={id:\"INC-035\",title:\"Rate limit exhaustion — 