{"type":"message","id":"9112654b","parentId":"e01e3864","timestamp":"2026-06-01T21:39:51.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done and pushed! Here's the summary:\n\n## Crew-New Port — Complete ✅\n\n**Ported files (8 libraries + 1 type change):**\n\n| File | What changed |\n|---|---|\n| `crew-sprites.ts` | NEW — canvas pixel-art draw functions (4 agents, 6 poses, procedural animation) |\n| `CrewSprite.tsx` | NEW — `<canvas>` sprite renderer with requestAnimationFrame loop |\n| `RoomCanvas.tsx` | Replaced — hand-drawn pixel art rooms with animated overlays |\n| `StationFloorplan.tsx` | Replaced — crew visits with L-shaped walking paths, EN ROUTE labels, bug-fixed duplicate sprite suppression |\n| `AgentOffice.tsx` | Replaced — wires live data into StationRoom per-agent, uses canvas sprites |\n| `AmbientStation.tsx` | Replaced — mood lighting (calm/busy/alert/critical), stars, drone couriers |\n| `RoomAmbient.tsx` | Replaced — per-room effects: coffee steam, radar, welder sparks, floating dust |\n| `CelebrationOverlay.tsx` | Replaced — 22-particle confetti with gradient sweep |\n| `crew.ts` | Modified — removed PNG sprite imports, `Sprites` type, `.sprites` field from CrewMember |\n\n**Integration points updated:**\n- `Dashboard.tsx` — now renders `<StationFloorplan>` with `<AgentOffice>` per crew member, wrapped in `<AmbientStation>` + `<CelebrationOverlay>`\n- `visual.tsx` — same wiring for the dedicated `/visual` page\n- `StationRoom.tsx` — uses `<CrewSprite>` instead of `<img src={agentSprite}>`\n- `TaskFlowSignals.tsx` — gradient uses `cyan-accent` class\n\n**Verification:**\n- ✅ TypeScript compiles (0 new errors)\n- ✅ All 11 routes return 200\n- ✅ No SSR runtime errors\n- ✅ Sprites render via `<canvas>` on Dashboard and `/visual`\n- ✅ Crew visits work (agents walk between rooms, home room hides sprite during visit)\n- ✅ Mood lighting responds to station state\n- ✅ All existing pages preserved (Tasks, Scheduler, Incidents, Settings, Teams, Memory, Activity, Docs, Projects)\n\n**Commit:** `a0e9dcd` pushed to GitHub."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":270,"output":510,"cacheRead":135296,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":0,"totalTokens":136076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780349970096,"responseId":"gen-1780349970-3bSljPw9ZWyWY8WYa3Cq"}}
