{"type":"message","id":"18c24eef","parentId":"94cbb401","timestamp":"2026-06-01T21:44:28.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There it is — `${accent}40` and `${accent}30`. The accent is an `oklch()` color string like `\"oklch(0.78 0.14 200)\"` and appending `40` produces `\"oklch(0.78 0.14 200)40\"` which is not a valid canvas color.\n\nLet me check all canvas draw calls across the affected files:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"afabe449-3166-4548-9d6d-0e0a22ff5020","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Issue #1: Find ALL canvas color usage patterns across the three files\necho \"=== StationRoom.tsx ===\"\ngrep -n \"ctx\\.\\|strokeStyle\\|fillStyle\\|accent\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx\n\necho \"=== RoomCanvas.tsx ===\"\ngrep -n \"ctx\\.\\|strokeStyle\\|fillStyle\\|fillRect\\|strokeRect\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/RoomCanvas.tsx | head -40\n\necho \"=== crew-sprites.ts ===\"\ngrep -n \"ctx\\.\\|strokeStyle\\|fillStyle\\|fillRect\\|strokeRect\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/crew-sprites.ts | head -40"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# Issue #1: Find ALL canvas color usage patterns across the three files\\necho \\\"=== StationRoom.tsx ===\\\"\\ngrep -n \\\"ctx\\\\.\\\\|strokeStyle\\\\|fillStyle\\\\|accent\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx\\n\\necho \\\"=== RoomCanvas.tsx ===\\\"\\ngrep -n \\\"ctx\\\\.\\\\|strokeStyle\\\\|fillStyle\\\\|fillRect\\\\|strokeRect\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/RoomCanvas.tsx | head -40\\n\\necho \\\"=== crew-sprites.ts ===\\\"\\ngrep -n \\\"ctx\\\\.\\\\|strokeStyle\\\\|fillStyle\\\\|fillRect\\\\|strokeRect\\\" ~/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/lib/crew-sprites.ts | head -40\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/owl-alpha","usage":{"input":90836,"output":272