{"type":"message","id":"be6dcab9","parentId":"41df06b7","timestamp":"2026-06-01T21:48:45.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"But the SSR hydration mismatch — the `useMemo` computes on server as `catch -> \"#6030c0\"` but on client might compute to a different hex. I need to suppress the radar canvas during SSR entirely. Let me use a `useState` + `useEffect` pattern for the accentHex to avoid hydration issues:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"8068471e-023e-41ce-8d5d-d6db3c4fc56e","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx","edits":[{"oldText":"  // Pre-compute hex color for canvas API (client-side only — canvas doesn't exist during SSR)\n  const accentHex = useMemo(() => {\n    try {\n      const c = document.createElement(\"canvas\");\n      c.width = c.height = 1;\n      const ctx2d = c.getContext(\"2d\")!;\n      ctx2d.fillStyle = accent;\n      ctx2d.fillRect(0, 0, 1, 1);\n      const [r, g, b] = ctx2d.getImageData(0, 0, 1, 1).data;\n      return \"#\" + [r, g, b].map(v => v.toString(16).padStart(2, \"0\")).join(\"\");\n    } catch { return \"#6030c0\"; }\n  }, [accent]);","newText":"  // Convert accent to hex for canvas API — done on client only to avoid SSR hydration mismatch\n  const [accentHex, setAccentHex] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  useEffect(() => {\n    try {\n      const c = document.createElement(\"canvas\");\n      c.width = c.height = 1;\n      const x = c.getContext(\"2d\")!;\n      x.fillStyle = accent;\n      x.fillRect(0, 0, 1, 1);\n      const [r, g, b] = x.getImageData(0, 0, 1, 1).data;\n      setAccentHex(\"#\" + [r, g, b].map(v => v.toString(16).padStart(2, \"0\")).join(\"\"));\n    } catch { setAccentHex(\"#6030c0\"); }\n  }, [accent]);"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/Users/spacemonkey/.openclaw/workspace/mission-control-dashboard/src/components/StationRoom.tsx\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"  // Pre-compute hex color 